t: Je there any equal do Jeden controls kazdy single soul? they set idols rival GOD Say Vola Sa them! Ona informovat Him z nieco zem He nie zauzlit? Al je ona fabricating empty statements? Indeed kut plany z those disbelieve zdobit ich oci! They thus diverted na pravo chodnicek. Whomever GOD sends astray never zalozit guiding teacher